eu.wauz.wauzcore.events

Class WauzPlayerEventQuestComplete

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.wauz.wauzcore.events.WauzPlayerEventQuestComplete
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WauzPlayerEvent

    public class WauzPlayerEventQuestComplete
extends java.lang.Object
implements WauzPlayerEvent
    An event that lets a player complete a quest and receive the rewards. The quest slot and the phase are cleared, the cooldown for daily quests gets reset, the quest completions increase, and finally an effect and the completion message is shown. After that the quest rewards are handed out.
    Author:
    Wauzmons
